#doc (Manual) "LeanModularForms Blueprint" =>

This blueprint documents the **LeanModularForms** project: the abstract theory of
Hecke rings and its specialisation to $`\mathrm{GL}_2`, Hecke operators on modular
forms, the Hungerbühler–Wasem generalised residue theorem, and the valence formula
for modular forms on $`\mathrm{SL}_2(\mathbb{Z})`.

